NAME: EM_ENABLE_FAILED
MESSAGE: VCU failed EM enable b/c: #data (Reasons: 0: bpsState false, 1: low brake pressure, 2: throttle non-zero, 3: brake not pressed, 4: not hv enabled, 5: motors failed to start)

NAME: EM_ENABLE_FAILED
MESSAGE: VCU failed EM enable b/c: #data (Reasons: 0: bpsState false, 1: low brake pressure, 2: throttle non-zero, 3: brake not pressed, 4: not hv enabled, 5: motors failed to start)

NAME: BOARDS_TURNING_OFF
MESSAGE: Critical failure occurred, PDU is about to turn off the boards after a short delay

NAME: BOARDS_OFF
MESSAGE: Critical failure occurred, PDU is turning off the boards

NAME: LV_CUTTOFF_BOARDS_OFF
MESSAGE: LV Cuttoff has been reached, PDU is about to turn off the boards after a short delay

NAME: PDU_HV_Critical
MESSAGE: HV Critical failure has been detected by the PDU

NAME: Brake_Pressure_FAIL
MESSAGE: Brake pressure sensor detected a failure

NAME: IMD_Failure
MESSAGE: IMD detected a fault. Value is of enum IMDStatus in imdDriver.h

NAME: WatchdogTaskMissedCheckIn
MESSAGE: Watchdog task detected that a task missed its checkin time, a watchdog reset is about to happen for the board

NAME: BMU_Charger_ERROR
MESSAGE: Charger reported an error while charging

NAME: BMU_SystemNotReady
MESSAGE: BMU is waiting for system to come up, and can't process the request yet (Reasons: 1: IMD_FAIL, 2: IL_HVIL_FAIL)

NAME: PDU_EM_EN_BLOCKED_DCDC_OFF
MESSAGE: PDU blocked EM enable request since DC-DC not on

NAME: BMU_UNKOWN_EVENT_STATE_COMBO
MESSAGE: BMU received an event for which it doesn't have a registered transition in the current state

NAME: BrakeWhileThrottleError_Disabled
MESSAGE: Max throttle while brake pressed reached, throttle disabled as per EV.3.4 (FSAE)

NAME: BrakeWhileThrottleError_Enabled
MESSAGE: Throttle reached reset point after BrakeWhileThrottle Error, Throttle Re engaged as per EV.3.4(FSAE)

NAME: MOTOR_CONTROLLERS_FAULT_OFF
MESSAGE: Motor controllers in fault off state

NAME: VCU_F7_NoTransition
MESSAGE: VCU: No state machine transition found
